  "content": "## Observability (D62)\n\n### Layer A: OTel Spans\n\n```\ncorvia.rag.query                      — parent span\n  ├─ corvia.rag.retrieve              — retrieval\n  │   ├─ corvia.rag.retrieve.vector   — vector search\n  │   ├─ corvia.rag.retrieve.graph    — graph expansion (if enabled)\n  │   └─ corvia.rag.retrieve.filter   — visibility + RBAC\n  ├─ corvia.rag.augment               — context assembly\n  └─ corvia.rag.generate              — GenerationEngine call (ask mode only)\n```\n\n\n### Layer A: Metrics\n\n| Type | Name | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| Counter | `corvia.rag.queries` | Total RAG queries |\n| Counter | `corvia.rag.context_only` | Queries in context-only mode |\n| Histogram | `corvia.rag.retrieve.duration_ms` | Retrieval latency |\n| Histogram | `corvia.rag.augment.duration_ms` | Context assembly latency |\n| Histogram | `corvia.rag.generate.duration_ms` | Generation latency |\n| Histogram | `corvia.rag.total.duration_ms` | End-to-end latency |\n| Histogram | `corvia.rag.context.tokens` | Token count of assembled context |\n| Counter | `corvia.rag.sources.included` | Entries included in context |\n| Counter | `corvia.rag.sources.truncated` | Entries that exceeded budget |\n",
